Package ca.phon.script.params.history

Class ParamHistoryManager

java.lang.Object
ca.phon.script.params.history.ParamHistoryManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
QueryHistoryManager
public class ParamHistoryManager
extends java.lang.Object
Manager for ParamHistoryType objects. This method provides the application logic for the generated JAXB classes. Methods in this class should be used for manipulating ParamHistoryTypes.
